// laceEmitRecovery example: no notification when already healthy.
//
// When the previous run was also successful, no recovery
// notification fires — there is no transition to report.
//
// Run:
//   lacelang-executor run no_recovery_when_stable.lace \
//     --enable-extension laceNotifications \
//     --enable-extension laceEmitRecovery \
//     --prev no_recovery_when_stable_prev.json --pretty
//
// Expected: 0 notifications.

get("https://httpbin.org/get")
.expect(status: 200)
